01:08.447 --> 01:09.781
You do look amazing.

01:09.781 --> 01:11.280
Philip.

01:11.322 --> 01:13.238
Hi!

01:13.280 --> 01:14.280
What are youdoing here?

01:15.447 --> 01:16.322
I had a deposition

01:16.364 --> 01:18.197
in the buildingacross the street.

01:18.239 --> 01:19.155
Oh...

01:19.197 --> 01:21.906
Carly, I coulduse some coffee.

01:23.948 --> 01:25.447
Sure.

01:25.447 --> 01:27.072
Thanks, Chloe.

01:28.072 --> 01:30.113
So...good surprise?

01:30.113 --> 01:31.781
Uh, of course, yeah.

01:31.781 --> 01:33.364
But right nowI have to go.

01:33.405 --> 01:34.822
Mr. St. Clair wants to see me.

01:34.864 --> 01:36.030
Do you thinkthat's a good thing?

01:36.072 --> 01:37.113
