You got your scholarship.

10:34.656 --> 10:36.614
That is,if you still want to go.

10:36.614 --> 10:38.280
Still want to go?

10:38.280 --> 10:39.322
Of course I do!

10:39.364 --> 10:40.280
I...I can't believe it.

10:40.322 --> 10:41.697
I'm going to Duke!

10:41.739 --> 10:42.739
I'm going todesign things.

10:42.781 --> 10:45.447
I'm going to bean architect.

10:45.489 --> 10:47.031
We are so happy for you.

10:48.113 --> 10:50.322
This is your dream.

10:50.364 --> 10:51.781
I... I can't believe it.

10:51.822 --> 10:52.864
I'm going to Duke!

10:52.906 --> 10:53.739
[brakes screeching]

10:55.822 --> 10:57.572
[sighs]

11:04.697 --> 11:06.113
I'm so sorry.

11:06.113 --> 11:07.781
I guess I got distracted.

11:13.489 --> 11:14.447
Joe?

11:14.489 --> 11:15.781
Megan?

11:22.405 --> 11:23.405
Well, doesn't look likethere's any damage.

11:27.989 --> 11:29.364
You okay?

11:29.405 --> 11:30.781
What?

11:30.822 --> 11:34.073
Well, you...you ran into me.

11:34.113 --> 11:35.155
Are you all right?

11:36.405 --> 11:37.948
I...

11:39.073 --> 11:40.113
Yes.

11:43.280 --> 11:45.656
Since when is therea stop sign here?

11:45.697 --> 11:47.197
Since a few months ago.

11:47.238 --> 11:48.906
Since when are youback in town?

11:48.948 --> 11:50.113
A few monthsbefore the stop sign.

11:51.280 --> 11:52.447
I came backto take over the farm

11:52.489 --> 11:54.031
after my dad retired.

11:54.073 --> 11:56.031
He and Momare traveling the world.

11:57.280 --> 11:58.948
So, you don't get homemuch, do you?

11:58.989 --> 12:00.447
What's that supposed to mean?

12:00.489 --> 12:01.489
Of course I do.

12:01.530 --> 12:02.656
I come home all the time.

12:02.697 --> 12:03.614
I was just here at Christmas.

12:03.614 --> 12:06.280
I talk to my dad,like, every day.

12:06.322 --> 12:07.656
