12:07.697 --> 12:09.322
I'm not sure.

12:09.364 --> 12:10.989
Anyway, um,if everything's good here,

12:11.031 --> 12:11.989
I'm probably gonna...

12:12.031 --> 12:12.864
uh, yeah,

12:12.906 --> 12:13.989
I'm gonna go.

12:14.031 --> 12:15.155
[chuckling]

12:15.197 --> 12:16.197
Megan...

12:17.948 --> 12:20.614
How are you?

12:20.614 --> 12:22.113
Great.

12:22.113 --> 12:23.155
Perfect.

12:23.197 --> 12:26.697
I have an amazing job,an amazing apartment,

12:26.739 --> 12:28.530
an amazing boyfriend.

12:28.572 --> 12:30.197
Basically, my life's...

12:30.239 --> 12:31.031
Amazing?

12:31.073 --> 12:32.781
Exactly.

12:33.948 --> 12:36.113
We're talking aboutgetting engaged.

12:36.113 --> 12:37.489
Congratulations.

12:37.530 --> 12:38.864
Thanks.

12:38.906 --> 12:40.781
And so you're...you're an architect?

12:40.781 --> 12:43.572
I, uh, I workin client relations

12:43.614 --> 12:45.113
at Stoneland.

12:45.113 --> 12:46.113
I'm sure you've heard of us.

12:46.155 --> 12:47.113
We're one of the biggestin our field.

12:47.155 --> 12:48.739
No, I... I haven't.

