Anyway, I'm a supervisor.

12:52.447 --> 12:54.447
So, you're...you're not an architect.

12:55.948 --> 12:56.948
What happened to your dream?

12:56.989 --> 13:00.280
I really need to go.

13:00.322 --> 13:01.948
I don't know if you heard,my dad's in the hospital.

13:01.948 --> 13:04.572
No, I-I did hear that.

13:04.614 --> 13:06.155
I actually wentto go see Matt this morning.

13:08.280 --> 13:09.781
Great.

13:09.781 --> 13:11.489
Well, goodbye.

13:15.948 --> 13:17.572
[engine starting]

13:26.656 --> 13:27.948
Well, that was fun.

13:27.948 --> 13:31.197
It's straight down here,and then a right on Elm Street.

13:32.781 --> 13:34.447
Dad!

13:34.447 --> 13:36.155
Oh, hey, honey,how you doing?

13:36.197 --> 13:37.656
Are you okay?

13:39.781 --> 13:41.113
I'm fine.

13:41.155 --> 13:42.656
I'll be outta herein no time.

13:42.697 --> 13:43.781
Dr. Baker says

13:43.781 --> 13:45.656
you were on thatbroken ladder again.

13:45.697 --> 13:47.614
You have no businessbeing up there.

