13:48.948 --> 13:50.280
You make me soundlike an old man.

13:50.280 --> 13:52.280
Mom would not have allowed it.

13:54.073 --> 13:55.948
Megan Quinn?

13:55.989 --> 13:58.781
Paging Megan Quinn.

13:58.822 --> 14:00.656
Violet! Hey.

14:01.864 --> 14:03.948
Oh, I was hopingyou'd be on call.

14:03.948 --> 14:05.280
How you feeling, Mr. Q?

14:05.280 --> 14:06.989
Bored, Violet.

14:07.031 --> 14:08.322
Hmm.

14:08.364 --> 14:09.864
Hey, have you beenby the café lately?

14:09.906 --> 14:12.447
